# StudyPad ğŸ“âœ¨

**4-key macropad for students with Pomodoro & Quick Notes**

StudyPad is a super compact 4-key macropad made for students who want to **focus and stay organized**.  
With just one touch, you can start or stop a Pomodoro, create quick notes, and open the Notes app.  

