## ğŸ“ Project Structure

- **CAD/** â†’ 3D case files (.STEP, .STP, .3MF)  
- **PCB/** â†’ PCB files (KiCAD)  
- **Firmware/** â†’ macropad firmware (`main.py`)  

---

## ğŸ”‘ Key Functions

| Key | Function |
|-----|---------|
| 1 | Start Pomodoro |
| 2 | Stop Pomodoro |
| 3 | Quick Note |
| 4 | Open Notes App |

---

## âš¡ How It Works

- Written in **KMK + CircuitPython** for **RP2040**  
- Each key sends **macros** simulating actions on the computer  
- Even without hardware, `main.py` shows the full logic of the macropad  

